text: Agdistis symmetrica is a moth in the family Pterophoridae. It is known from the Malta and Tunisia. The wingspan is about 20 mm.Die palaearktischen Agdistis -Arten (Lepidoptera, Pterophoridae) ==References== Category:Agdistinae Category:Taxa named by Hans Georg Amsel Category:Moths described in 1955
